verses.verse: Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye the <S%H3050>LORD.<s%> <S%H1984>Praise,<s%> O ye <S%H5650>servants<s%> of the <S%H3068>LORD,<s%> <S%H1984>praise<s%> <S%H853><s%> the <S%H8034>name<s%> of the <S%H3068>LORD.<s%>

That he may <S%H3427>set<s%> him <S%H5973>with<s%> <S%H5081>princes,<s%> even <S%H5973>with<s%> the <S%H5081>princes<s%> of his <S%H5971>people.<s%>
